{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-011__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-011", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-011__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·011.1", "text_original": "蘀兮蘀兮，風其吹女。叔兮伯兮，倡予和女。\n蘀兮蘀兮，風其漂女。叔兮伯兮，倡予要女。", "text_normalized": "蘀兮蘀兮，風其吹女。叔兮伯兮，倡予和女。\n蘀兮蘀兮，風其漂女。叔兮伯兮，倡予要女。", "notes": "蘀兮 Chinese poem 1."}
